Dave C. Bolen sends:

> what the heck is a "Riviera".

It's a camper. Kinda like a Westfalia, but converted by a company in Oregon.

Quick ID hints: top comes up straight instead of at an angle, and (if the PO
didn't remove it) there's a little approval plate under the passenger's cab
door from the State of Oregon Recreational Vehicle Section.
